540
00:37:15,773 --> 00:37:20,233
Once I break free, I'll slice you into a million pieces.

541
00:37:21,453 --> 00:37:25,292
Murong Fu, what are you waiting for?

542
00:37:25,292 --> 00:37:29,052
Pierce her body. Kill her now.

543
00:37:29,052 --> 00:37:30,833
Duan.

544
00:37:31,673 --> 00:37:36,413
Did you forget what you...

545
00:37:37,233 --> 00:37:39,713
used to tell me?

546
00:37:41,913 --> 00:37:44,133
It's been so many years.

547
00:37:45,093 --> 00:37:47,993
We were apart

548
00:37:47,993 --> 00:37:51,113
and now, we can finally see each other.

549
00:37:51,713 --> 00:37:53,393
You...

550
00:37:54,513 --> 00:37:58,373
Yet you say such harsh words to me.

551
00:38:00,333 --> 00:38:03,973
Our daughter, Yuyan,

552
00:38:05,193 --> 00:38:07,493
have you seen her?

553
00:38:10,253 --> 00:38:12,753
Do you love me? Tell me.

554
00:38:12,753 --> 00:38:16,593
More than a decade ago, we severed ties.

555
00:38:16,593 --> 00:38:18,793
Nothing remains.

556
00:38:18,793 --> 00:38:21,413
Don't bring the past up again.

557
00:38:21,413 --> 00:38:25,753
Fu'er, give me the antidote.

558
00:38:27,513 --> 00:38:30,693
I want to kill this heartless man.

559
00:38:33,013 --> 00:38:34,553
Aunt.

560
00:38:44,813 --> 00:38:46,633
Tell me.

561
00:38:47,513 --> 00:38:49,813
