579
00:40:20,353 --> 00:40:25,533
Of course. I remember.

580
00:40:25,533 --> 00:40:28,112
We'll go tomorrow.

581
00:40:28,112 --> 00:40:33,573
Tomorrow, we'll visit the jade sculpture of your mother.

582
00:40:41,013 --> 00:40:43,153
Can you picture it?

583
00:40:44,733 --> 00:40:47,053
Over that jade wall,

584
00:40:52,593 --> 00:40:56,733
